item.description: Hey guys my b-day is tomorrow. It is Tuesday so everything is kind of dead, so I want to celebrate in in a very low key, calm energy manner. My friend owns a pool/restaurant bar type place in Colchester, and that is where I am from, so if you guys want to come down, hang out, play some pool, drink some beer and bullshit come down you are very welcome to come
item.name: Ace's Birthday (Low key event)
